caption:
Hey nurse besties, if you haven’t already, make sure to enter for your chance to win some seriously awesome prizes during Nurses Week! This year, we’re not only filling your pockets and satisfying your taste buds but also giving you the glow-up you deserve!

❤️ 40 lucky nurses will get a $25 Subway gift card—perfect for a quick, delicious meal!
❤️ 40 winners will receive a CeraVe gift box valued at $100
❤️ 20 grand prize winners will take home a $100 AmEx gift card

👉 Comment in the chat and let us know what your favorite Nurses Week gift has been! 

Giveaway is not associated with Meta. Giveaway closes 5/12 2359 EST. Winners will be contacted after the giveaway period closes via email. Winners must be located in the United States and must be 18 years or older at the time of entry. By entering, you agree to The Nursing Beat’s Terms & Conditions.
